A '''semantic broker''' is a computer service that automatically provides [[semantic mapper]] services.  A semantic broker is frequently part of a semantic [[middleware]] system that leverage semantic equivalence statements. To qualify as a semantic broker product a system must be able to automatically extract data from a message and use semantic equvalance statements to transform this into another namespace.

